high_descs: Turn around to face the white box.
Pick up the toilet paper roll off of the white box.
Turn around and walk forward, then hang a right and walk over to the toilet.
Put the toilet paper roll on the front right edge of the toilet tank.
Turn left and walk forward, then turn left and walk up to the door. turn right and walk up to the white table.
Pick up the toilet paper roll off of the table.
Walk over to the toilet.
Put the toilet paper roll on the toilet tank.
anns.task_desc: Move two toilet paper rolls to the toilet tank.

high_descs: Walk towards the table
Grab a toilet paper from the table
Walk towards the toilet
Put the toilet paper on top of the toilet
Walk towards the large table
Grab an empty roll of toilet paper from the table
Walk towards the toilet
Put the empty toilet paper roll on top of the toilet
anns.task_desc: Grab a toilet paper, empty toilet paper roll, put them on top of the toilet

high_descs: Move right facing the top of the white cabinet where the toilet paper is
Pick up the toilet paper roll on the cabinet
Carry the toilet paper roll over to the toilet in the right corner of the bathroom
Place the toilet paper on the back of the toilet tank on the right side
Move across the room to the large white counter under the mirror
Pick up the brown tube on top of the counter on the left side
Carry the brown tube back to the toilet tank where the toilet paper was placed
Place the brown tube on the toilet tank to the left of the toilet paper
anns.task_desc: Move a roll of toilet paper and an empty cardboard roll to the toilet tank
